Season 5
As the fifth season was taped at the 2025 Just for Laughs festival, the season's broadcast dates and episode order have not yet been confirmed. The following roast battles were staged during the taping:
*Allie Pearse vs Jeff McEnery
*Che Durena vs Jacob Balshin
*Faris Hytiaa vs Dino Archie
*Jon Dore vs Rebecca Kohler
*Andrea Jin vs Alistair Ogden
*Tranna Wintour vs Sam Sferrazza
